_:N2ae3d21a59114acf8197ba81f8fcd0fe <http://schema.org/description> "We scrutinise new free trade agreements (FTAs) once they are signed. We are independent of the Department for Business and Trade (DBT) and DBT ministers play no part in the TAC’s advice on FTAs. However, we are supported by a small Secretariat, which is based in DBT." .
